title: Duke Ellington - Live! at the Newport Jazz Festival '59
description:
DUKE ELLINGTON - LIVE! AT THE NEWPORT JAZZ FESTIVAL '59

02. Idiom '59

Duke Ellington & His Orchestra
Cat Anderson, Harold "Shorty" Baker, Fats Ford, Willie Cook, Clark Terry (tp), Ray Nance (tp, vln, vcl), Quentin Jackson (tb), Britt Woodman, John Sanders (tb), Jimmy Hamilton (cl, ts), Russell Procope (cl, as, ww on "Jones"), Johnny Hodges (as), Paul Gonsalves (ts), Harry Carney (bar, cl, b-cl), Duke Ellington (p), Jimmy Woode (b), Sam Woodyard, Jimmy Johnson (d)
Recorded live at the Newport Jazz Festival, Newport, Rhode Island, July 4, 1959

As there are no liner notes or personnel or really anything useful other than composer credits on the scans I extrapolated the personnel above from my FESTIVAL SESSION upload.
